-----Deathrun_sk_jail_v3----

Big Deathrun many traps.     
---Info---

over 25 traps.
2 Secret.
52 CT 
2 T MAX!
Map its Hard or medium map type.  (and very hard for nubs)
CT must run to the end, and select one of the options to kill the T'S The hard way or the easy way.

----Secret----

The Secret button. (if you have play the map you know)   its a secret button, but  you CANT use Noclip to get in, you will be teleport to a room (NOOB-ROOM). where there its no escape (only if admin teleport you out, or write "kill" in console)   ITS NOT A SECRET, IF YOU GET TELEPORT. There s only one way to press that button and that is to open the door!!.   By the way the door can only be open by a secret button in the map. 

The other secret is only for the CT  its a  Super ak44. in the end, but have to get it??
 
----Traps----

-Spikes, Crusher, Explosion, Rocket launcher, Laser, Lightning, Fan, Teleport, and mush, mush more.
